{"tid":2287920,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"祖瑟夫再發功撐香港","createTime":"2020-11-16T06:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T06:46:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f667b9afe351c15bf011d39717a6a03a240871ce","tid":2287920,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T06:31:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201116/XMQAQ4G465AKHDMEHK3R3R7A5A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201116%2FXMQAQ4G465AKHDMEHK3R3R7A5A%2F&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3j4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=d98fe7ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201116%2FXMQAQ4G465AKHDMEHK3R3R7A5A%2F&h=e797bf2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201116/XMQAQ4G465AKHDMEHK3R3R7A5A/</a><br />\n<br />\n祖瑟夫再發功撐香港<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bBrQufpQ1jviR83OyTcOn0aAq4M=/960x640/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/M6HOJSXW4ZDPNLZPH5F22VIDXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbBrQufpQ1jviR83OyTcOn0aAq4M%3D%2F960x640%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FM6HOJSXW4ZDPNLZPH5F22VIDXM.jpg&h=2d2356e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大量網民向祖瑟夫道謝，感謝他關注香港。<br />\n<br />\n荷李活型男祖瑟夫哥頓利域（Joseph Gordon-Levitt）在8月底開始炮製與香港有關的創作，上月又再次在fb呼籲香港人讀出撐港詩《香港永不眠》（Hong Kong Never Sleeps），其後公開包含大量反修例運動片段和照片的撐港短片。<br />\n<br />\n前日男神再度發功，他表示：「一位hitRECord的成員創作了一個新計劃，叫『Stand with Hong Kong』，他們正找一位寫作人去回應一句句子。」召集網民填充完成「Stand with Hong Kong for ______________」這句句子，引來不少人回應「自由」、「公義」、「民主」等字句。昨日，祖瑟夫又再邀網民讀出關於香港的句子，當中寫道：「當我孤單時看到香港的光，它讓我感到活着，在和平與不安之中&hellip;&hellip;但是在好的方面。」<br />\n<br />\n===========<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e4f3e7058c0cbd5f9c95ea5f1e92a0b781a754","tid":2287920,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T06:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"}]}